    "Various applications for GANs including image editing and synthesis, image translations as well as audio enhancement and synthesis using the reserves from the GAN models are discussed in section 6.",
    "Section 7 identifies different evaluation parameters like FID and IS as major parameters used for evaluation of GAN models that help to improve its performance.",
    "Various types of available datasets are discussed in section 8.",
    "Section 9 discusses the various research findings and discussion about the review.",
    "Section 10 finally conclude this review study."
